				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">/veto.
<br />

<br />
This is not at all what we need.  We need to be outdamaging wizards and rogues in most situations by a good margin assuming similar gear.  Thats what we need.  How do I want it done?  Pets scaling with mana - the more mana you have the better your pet (more hps/ac/atk/max hit).  I've said it a million times, there are no forseeable downsides to this, and it would give the high end mages the power they need to compete with the content they face, while giving the casual magicians the small upgrade they need to stay on top of wizards and rogues.
<br />

